---
description: Claim safety rules for AI API Ops.
globs: src/**,public/**
alwaysApply: false
---

Banned claims:

- cheapest
- guaranteed compatible
- official partner
- all models available
- unlimited generation
- no billing risk
- no failed-generation cost
- RutaAPI supports every model mentioned
- Sora/Veo/Kling/Runway/Seedance always available through RutaAPI

Required safe wording:

- check live model pricing
- model availability can change
- test small before scaling
- media generation pricing may be per token, credit, second, image, video or async task
- failed generations and retries should be checked in request logs and provider dashboards
- agent workflows can multiply token usage through long context, retries, tool calls and automation
